{"tid":700009,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日拘多名中國人　涉違法保管處方藥　疑向陸客銷售","createTime":"2018-06-13T03:54:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T04:16:36.000Z","uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d7442308b5325f59ad4bd4f708fc1210bc318c2b","tid":700009,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T03:54:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/news_aoHvt_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fnews_aoHvt_1200x0.png&h=5b9e0816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本共同社報道，大阪府警生活環境課近日以涉嫌以銷售為目的持有需要處方的醫藥品、違反《醫藥品醫療器械法》（以銷售為目的貯存）為由，逮捕了經營貿易公司的張金利（35歲，居住在堺市堺區）等8名中國人和1名日籍公司女董事。據悉，他們可能是為了向中國遊客銷售而保管了處方藥。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述辦案相關🇨🇳人員🇨🇳透露，日本產醫藥品在中國被稱為「神藥」，很有人氣，特別是處方藥被高價出售。警方認為出於這樣的需求，有業界人士把藥暗中倒賣給了張金利等人，正在展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n此外被逮捕的是經營另一家貿易公司的李鵬（28歲，居住在大阪市中央區）及中國留學生等。<br />\n<br />\n大阪府警生活環境課指，涉嫌人在中國的免費通訊應用程式（APP）上發佈寫有日本住址的身份證，宣揚可以拿到日本產醫藥品，還在大阪市內的藥妝店招呼中國遊客進行兜售。<br />\n<br />\n被捕的嫌疑人涉嫌5月下旬在沒有藥局開設許可的情況下，以銷售為目的保管有去除幽門螺旋桿菌和治療高血壓的藥品等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%97%A5%E6%8B%98%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E6%B6%89%E9%81%95%E6%B3%95%E4%BF%9D%E7%AE%A1%E8%99%95%E6%96%B9%E8%97%A5%E7%96%91%E5%90%91%E9%99%B8%E5%AE%A2%E9%8A%B7%E5%94%AE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%258B%2598%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2590%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B6%2589%25E9%2581%2595%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25BF%259D%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E8%2599%2595%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%2597%25A5%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%2590%2591%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E9%258A%25B7%25E5%2594%25AE%2F&d=8RTelL83%2BhILtVv%2FCeYAPqS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=a6eee97d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%258B%2598%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2590%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B6%2589%25E9%2581%2595%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25BF%259D%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E8%2599%2595%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%2597%25A5%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%2590%2591%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E9%258A%25B7%25E5%2594%25AE%2F&h=4fd9aa83\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%97%A5%E6%8B%98%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E6%B6%89%E9%81%95%E6%B3%95%E4%BF%9D%E7%AE%A1%E8%99%95%E6%96%B9%E8%97%A5%E7%96%91%E5%90%91%E9%99%B8%E5%AE%A2%E9%8A%B7%E5%94%AE/</a>"},{"pid":"5488df805173dc8e3493c0419dfa6363231af67d","tid":700009,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T03:57:21.000Z","msg":"支那人呃支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc5bb9f6687e83970de4fb172ab54d3de28d220","tid":700009,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T04:16:36.000Z","msg":"旅行團最中意賣呢啲散裝藥"}]}